				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%E1%BA%BF-L%C3%A2n/B%C3%ACnh-h%E1%BB%93-l%E1%BB%99ng-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-1vWtjdPgPqrPw1BXVFtdUw">Bình hồ lộng nguyệt - 平湖弄月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%E1%BA%BF-L%C3%A2n/author-ZqTE_3GO97Ws9hNrgzlGIw">Ngô Thế Lân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Xoa/Di%C3%AAu-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i-%C3%A1i-d%E1%BB%AF-ti%E1%BB%83u-ki%E1%BA%BFm-nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BA%B7ng/poem-IemaUEM6Da1UaFZrrkmZkA">Diêu tú tài ái dữ tiểu kiếm nhân tặng - 姚秀才愛予小劍因贈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Xoa/author-YOFLDe3VzkSorn9hMWnkGw">Lưu Xoa</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/%C4%90%C6%A1n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-d%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c-m%C3%A3-%C4%90%C3%A0n-Kh%C3%AA-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-E2oGXP8gWU0x0qw7jKOVsA">Đơn vịnh dược mã Đàn Khê sự - 單詠躍馬檀溪事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%BD-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-Ch%C3%A2u-Gi%E1%BA%A3-t%C6%B0-m%C3%A3-l%E1%BB%A5c-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Ba-Ch%C3%A2u-Nghi%C3%AAm-b%C3%A1t-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-l%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-c%C3%A1c-l%C3%A3o-ng%C5%A9-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-EIg64qLyc1Dqi6QQkVPfZQ">Ký Nhạc Châu Giả tư mã lục trượng, Ba Châu Nghiêm bát sứ quân lưỡng các lão ngũ thập vận - 寄岳州賈司馬六丈、巴州嚴八使君兩閣老五十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/L%C3%A2m-giang-ti%C3%AAn/poem-vokPQbddJabwsXCQP0m3Xw">Lâm giang tiên - 臨江仙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-l%C3%A2u-xu%C3%A2n/poem-KDsrFdwTObzKwClurZ9-PA">Ngọc lâu xuân - 玉樓春</a> (<